---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Sichos HaRan - Conversations of Rabbi Nachman" description="Informal conversations and teachings recorded by Rabbi Nachman's students">
  <section class="page-header">
    <h1>Sichos HaRan</h1>
    <p>שיחות הר"ן</p>
    <a href="/teachings" class="back-link">← Back to Teachings</a>
  </section>

  <section class="intro">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="description">
        <strong>Sichos HaRan</strong> (Conversations of Rabbi Nachman) contains informal conversations 
        and teachings that were recorded by Rebbe Nachman's students. Unlike the structured Torah 
        lessons of Likutay Moharan, these conversations capture Rebbe Nachman's spontaneous wisdom, 
        personal advice, and intimate teachings as he interacted with his followers on a daily basis.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="topics">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Topics Covered</h2>
      <div class="topics-grid">
        <div class="topic-card">
          <h3>Prayer & Devotion</h3>
          <p>Personal conversations about hitbodedut (self-seclusion) and heartfelt prayer</p>
        </div>
        <div class="topic-card">
          <h3>Joy & Happiness</h3>
          <p>The importance of joy in serving Hashem and overcoming sadness</p>
        </div>
        <div class="topic-card">
          <h3>Faith & Trust</h3>
          <p>Building unwavering faith in Hashem's providence</p>
        </div>
        <div class="topic-card">
          <h3>Perseverance</h3>
          <p>Never giving up, no matter how difficult the circumstances</p>
        </div>
        <div class="topic-card">
          <h3>Hope & Redemption</h3>
          <p>The power of hope and the promise of redemption</p>
        </div>
        <div class="topic-card">
          <h3>Daily Life</h3>
          <p>Practical guidance for navigating everyday challenges</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="famous-sayings">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Famous Teachings from Sichos</h2>
      <div class="sayings-list">
        <div class="saying-item">
          <p class="hebrew">כל העולם כולו גשר צר מאד והעיקר לא לפחד כלל</p>
          <p>"The whole world is a very narrow bridge, and the main thing is not to fear at all."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="saying-item">
          <p class="hebrew">אין שום דבר שאין בו תקווה</p>
          <p>"There is nothing without hope."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="saying-item">
          <p class="hebrew">אם אתה מאמין שאתה יכול לקלקל, תאמין שאתה יכול לתקן</p>
          <p>"If you believe you can damage, believe you can fix."</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="navigation">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>More Teachings</h2>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/teachings/likutay-eitzos" class="nav-link">Likutay Eitzos →</a>
        <a href="/teachings/shivchay-moharan" class="nav-link">Shivchay Moharan →</a>
        <a href="/teachings/sefer-hamidos" class="nav-link">Sefer HaMidos →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #553c9a 0%, #6b46c1 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-hebrew);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid white;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .intro {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: #f7f5f0;
  }

  .description {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #444;
  }

  .topics {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .topics h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .topics-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .topic-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    border-left: 4px solid #6b46c1;
  }

  .topic-card h3 {
    color: #553c9a;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .topic-card p {
    color: #666;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .famous-sayings {
    background: #faf5ff;
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .famous-sayings h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .sayings-list {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .saying-item {
    background: white;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }

  .saying-item .hebrew {
    font-family: var(--font-hebrew);
    color: #553c9a;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .saying-item p:last-child {
    color: #666;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .navigation {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: #f7f5f0;
  }

  .navigation h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .nav-link {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 6px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    transition: transform 0.3s;
  }

  .nav-link:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
</style>
